
REFERENCE: Game Servers

The Internet game servers are places accesssible by telnet where you can
play innumerable players, both human and machine, from all over the world. 
You can connect to one of the servers with the command: 

                  telnet <host machine's address> <port number>

(Please be careful not to include the angle brackets "< >".)

